quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  48,10,jo log tum se baet karte hain woh khuda se baet karte hain. khuda ka haath un ke hathon par hai. phir jo ehad ko torrey to ehad tornay ka nuqsaan isi ko hai. aur jo is baat ko jis ka is ne khuda se ehadkiya hai poora kere to woh usay anqareeb ajar azeem day ga
  48,11,jo ganwar peechay reh gay woh tum se kahin ge ke hum ko hamaray maal aur ahal vayal ne rok rakha aap hamaray liye ( khuda se ) bakhshish mangeen. yeh log apni zabaan se woh baat kehte hain jo un ke dil mein nahi hai. keh do ke agar khuda tum ( logon ) ko nuqsaan pahunchana chahay ya tumhe faida pohanchanay ka iradah farmaiye to kon hai jo is ke samnay tumahray liye kisi baat ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhay ( koi nahi ) balkay jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is se waaqif hai
  48,12,baat yeh hai ke tum log yeh samajh baithy they ke paighambar aur momin apne ahal vayal mein kabhi lout kar anay hi ke nahi. aur yahi baat tumahray dilon ko achi maloom hui. aur ( isi wajah se ) tum ne buray buray khayaal kiye aur ( aakhir kaar ) tum halakat mein par gay
  48,13,aur jo shakhs khuda par aur is ke paighambar par imaan nah laaye to hum ne ( aisay ) kafiroon ke liye aag tayyar kar rakhi hai
  48,14,aur asmano aur zameen ki badshahi khuda hi ki hai. woh jisay chahay bakhshay aur jisay chahay saza day. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  48,15,jab tum log ghanimatainlainay chalo ge to jo log peechay reh gay they woh kahin ge hamein bhi ijazat dijiye ke aap ke sath chalein. yeh chahtay hain ke khuda ke qoul ko badal den. keh do ke tum hargiz hamaray sath nahi chal satke. isi terhan khuda ne pehlay se farma diya hai. phir kahin ge ( nahi ) tum to hum se hasad karte ho. baat yeh hai ke yeh log samajte hi nahi magar bohat kam
